				that.helpcenter.xieyi38 = '7.1.3 Because of storms, earthquakes, tsunamis, floods, electricity, quenching wars, terrorist attacks, etc. which are force majeure causing the system to cause obstacles to not be able to operate the transaction;'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi39 = '7.1.4 Due to hacker attacks, techniques modification or a flaw of Telecommunications Department and other information related departments, website upgrade, banking issues and other reasons causing service interruption to be delayed.'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi40 = '7.2 During this agreement entered into force, In case there are the announcements of officials or related government agencies including amendments to the laws or policies resulting from government announcements that prevent Company from providing services under this agreement, such as if the law changes or announcements by government officials or government agencies regarding changes in rules or regulations related to the Company\'s business which shall be considered effective immediately from the effective date, it will not be considered as the Company breach of contract；'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi41 = '7.3 In case of business necessity of the Company, the Company has the right to stop providing services to User in accordance with the risks and economic situations that affect the business operations of the Company causing the Company to not be able to run the business and the Company is not able to provide services to User in any way or the service has been restricted to be used the service, it will not be considered as the Company breach of contract.'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi42 = '8. Intellectual Property Rights'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi43 = '8.1 All details and content appearing on the electronic operating systems of the Company, regardless of any other data, compositions, images, files, news, architecture of website or application, content arrangement or the story on the screen of the website or application, design of website or application, are the sole intellectual property rights of the Company. The rights under this clause are not limited to trademark rights, it also includes patents, petty patents, copyright and trade secrets etc.'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi44 = '8.2 No User or anyone will arbitrary use, modify, copy, publish, change, distribute, sell, transfer, or print the program or content that appears on the website or application. Except with the written consent of the company or other right holders are allowed to do so.'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi45 = '9. Governing law and dispute resolution'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi46 = '9.1 Thai law will be applicable with these terms, conditions or agreements and in the event that a dispute arises between User and the Company.'
				that.helpcenter.xieyi47 = '9.2 In case of any disputes occurred due to agreement content or performance, both parties shall make friendly negotiation in order to resolve the dispute. If the negotiation cannot be reached, either party can bring the case to the court with jurisdiction.'
